William 'Wild Bill' Wilson and his wife Lillian Karr Wilson died just two minutes apart from each other this week . 
  Both were Alzheimer's patients and had to live in separate nursing homes . 
  The couple first met in Corbin, Kentucky and were high school sweethearts . 
  According to their son Doug, they ran off to get married without their parents' blessing . 
  Bill was known for his radio show and Lillian for her work . 
 